comment: RATR shows that Hill (IND) cleanly strips the ball from Adams (OKC).

George (IND) legally contests Durant (OKC)'s jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Waiters (OKC) makes incidental contact with Ellis (IND) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Turner (IND) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Westbrook (OKC) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Durant (OKC) commits a take foul on George (IND).
Westbrook (OKC) commits a take foul on George (IND).
